Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在治疗中心的时间开心吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Did you enjoy your time at the treatment centre?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:06.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果你不坦白 你就会被带到那里去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cos that's where you're headed if you don't confess.
