Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:14.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我又感觉到了 我没有变得狂暴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I feel it again! I'm not turning rabid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:19.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-你害怕我 -我都认不出你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- You're scared of me? - I don't even recognise you any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是真实的我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:23.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:25.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我没法在他那样的时候看着他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can't look at him when he's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:27.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 上帝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:32.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我在找Simon 你看到他了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm looking for Simon. Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:35.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是你看到的第一个从坟墓里复活的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's the first person you saw rise from their grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:39.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我是Simon 我准备要跟随他了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's Simon. I'm ready to follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:42.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一切都需要来了了结了 Simon\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It has to be done, Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:45.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你必须杀掉第一个复活的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You must sacrifice the First Risen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在她复活的第12个月12日的12点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}on the 12th hour of the 12th day of the 12th month.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:50.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,第一个复活者必须被杀掉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The First Risen must be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:53.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这样 第二次重生才得以实现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Only then can the second resurrection occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:00:57.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:18.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们好 今天由我为你们服务 我是一个符合安全标准的半死症患者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hello. I'll be your waitress today. I'm a fully compliant PDS sufferer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,过去的24小时之内我已经注射过神经抑制剂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have been administered Neurotriptyline in the last 24 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:23.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,并且不会进入狂暴状态\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and will not enter a rabid state.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:26.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 哈哈 真是个好消息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh. Ha-ha. That's good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:28.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,茶还是咖啡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tea or coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:30.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,咖啡吧 谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Er... coffee, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:33.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:38.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么都不想吃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't fancy anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:42.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,离我们到达诺顿村 还有三个小时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Still got three hours ahead of us till we reach Roarton.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我是一个不吃早饭的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not a breakfast person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:46.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 这是一日三餐中最重要的一餐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, it's the most important meal of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:50.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你会需要这一餐的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're going to need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:53.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,采集可不是一件容易事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Collections never go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:59.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,往往造成一场激战\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Always put up a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不介意剩下的路我来开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't mind driving the rest of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:05.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你会发现这是个错误选择\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right, it's your funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:08.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,到了12月12号 你们就都会知道那意味着什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to 12th December, and you all know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:39.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,诺顿村的冬祭表演就快要来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Roarton Village's winter fête extravaganza is upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了 爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's going on, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:55.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我和你妈妈做了一个决定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Me and your mum have come to a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:56.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-什么决定 -嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- A decision? - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们觉得这个样子最好 万无一失\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, we think it's best, all things considered,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:02.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让理事会 你知道的 做他们要做的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to let the council, you know, do what they're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:04.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你 你要让他们再把我带回诺福克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You... you're letting them send me back to Norfolk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:06.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,回到那个治疗中心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Going back to t'treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可能只是医生安排的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}centre might be just what the doctor ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:08.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:12.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们接受过足够多的训练来应对这样的情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They're trained up to handle situations like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:15.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们能帮助你们变回原来正常的自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They'll be able to help you get back to your normal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是正常的我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is my normal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:19.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 是时候听听专业意见了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hm. It's time for a professional opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以 你 你就不再管我了么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So, you're... you're washing your hands of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:25.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我们在做我们确信能够让你收获最大利益的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. We're doing what we believe is in your best interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:28.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把我锁在我的卧室里 直到穿白色棉袄的男人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Locking me in my bedroom until the men in white coats
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:28.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,出现然后把我拖走吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}come along and drag me away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那 那就是最大利益么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That... that's in my best interests?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:34.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对了 我不希望他们是把你拖走的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, I hope they won't have to drag you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,至少 我可以打个电话给Amy吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can I call Amy, at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:37.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她也是那一伙的其中一员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She's part of the crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:39.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那已经对你造成了很不好的影响\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that's been having a bad influence on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是 我必须要跟她通话 爸爸 有些事情感觉不对劲了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, I need to speak to her, Dad. Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:43.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很担心她 爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm worried about her, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你吃完早饭后可以下来开始你的尖锐批评 可以吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You can come down for your shot after breakfast, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:48.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:50.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
