Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:11.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Jem 你准备好巡逻区域了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Jem? You getting ready to beat the bounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:41.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也不是很确定 Amy\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not entirely sure, Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:44.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就好像是你的身体在觉醒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It seems like your body's waking up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:47.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或是活过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or coming alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或是那之类的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:51.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为什么是我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:57.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-可能是因为你比较特别 -特别\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Maybe you're special. - Special?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我奶奶经常说我很特别\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My nan always said I was special,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我设想那只是我奶奶说的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but I just figured that's something all nans say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:07.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Philip 我要崩溃了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Philip, I'm freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:10.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 嘿 没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey. Hey, hey. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没事的 你很正常\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's all right. You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:15.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该寻找一些这方面的合适的医嘱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe we should get some proper medical advice on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去Russo那里看一下 你觉得如何\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}See Dr Russo. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 馊主意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得会发生什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do you think would
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:27.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们告诉Russo医生我在改变\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}happen if we told Dr Russo I was... changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得他会只轻拍我的背\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you think he'd just pat me on the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,给我一个棒棒糖 然后就让我走吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}give me a lolly and send me on my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他一定会通知治疗中心的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He'd call the treatment centre,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后他们就会带走我 在我身上做实验\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and then they'd cart me off to experiment on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道那种生活是怎么样的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know what the living are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:41.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道那些生活是怎么样的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know what some of the living are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须得保守这个秘密\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Got to keep this under our hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们不能就这么待在这-为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- We can't just stay here. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们会被冻死的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We'll die of hypothermia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你冷嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不冷嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我都冻僵了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听 你听 我的牙齿都在打颤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Listen, listen. My teeth are chattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈 别让他们带我去那\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mum, don't let them take me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Kier 综合考虑一切之后 只有这样最好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's for the best, Kier, all things considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可是他们会把我当做抵抗者的 那就不好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not if they take me back as a non-compliant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:48.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我不会再干任何蠢事了 好嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look, Dad, I'm not going to do anything stupid, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你以前也这么说 但之后你就惹了大麻烦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You've said that before, then it all goes horribly wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就这么定了 离开一段时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. Spending a bit of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:56.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,待在Norfolk 会让你状态好很多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}time in Norfolk will do you a tonne of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在那他们知道怎么对付你 对吧 Sue\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They know how to take care of you there, don't they, Sue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你睁眼瞎嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:02.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道让他们带我去治疗中心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know what's going to happen to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们会如何对我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if they take me back to the treatment centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要迟到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:07.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你会去参加活动纪念嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you coming to the fête, Steve?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我说过我会带Jem去游行 -好 待会见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I've said I'll take Jem to t'march. - Ok, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Kier 我们晚一点回来给你送行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Kier, we'll be back later to see you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 那好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh. All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那行 Kier 回你的房间待着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right, Kier, back to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我能把这个带上去嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can I take this up with me, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:24.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,诺顿早报\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Parish newsletter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只是消磨时间用的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Reading material.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:07.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,神爱世人 赐独子于凡尘\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For He so loved the world, that He gave His one and only Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,使信之者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Whoever shall believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不至灭亡 反得永生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}him shall not perish but have eternal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,引我避诱惑 救我离罪恶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Lead us not into temptation but deliver us from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:16.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,赐予我勇气 以终我宿命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Give me the courage to do my duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:20.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,庇护我家园 免遭于灾难\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to protect and defend my community from all harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,帮帮我吧 上帝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So help me God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:41.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Simon\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Simon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:47.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,今天重生之时会是怎样的景象\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}When the dead rise today, what will they be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,第二次重生 会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The Second Risen will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:55.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 会发生一些变化\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, they're going to change things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,将会终结\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They're going to bring
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,苦难与迫害\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}an end to the suffering and the persecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,第二次重生后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}After the second Rising,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:02.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们不会再被唾弃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we ain't going to be treated like dirt any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:05.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们能帮忙嘛 Simon\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can we help you do it, Simon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我必须独自完成一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I've got to do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:10.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 那我们要做什么 -做好心理准备\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Well, what should we do? - Prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:19.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,主啊 让信徒们完成今天的使命吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Lord, let the disciple complete his mission today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Martin小姐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Miss Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我准备好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:31.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只要你开口 我就去清除威胁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To stop the threat. Just say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:34.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谁是威胁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Who's the threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爱尔兰半死人 那个复生解放军极端分子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The Irish rotter. The ULA extremist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,别管他 队长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Leave it alone, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:44.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你说什么 他在策划袭击啊 Martin小姐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What you saying? He's planning an attack, Miss Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你有证据嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where's your proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:50.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,证据 不是你告诉我的嘛 你叫我跟踪他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Proof? You said it yourself. You got me to follow him and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:51.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但你什么也没发现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And nothing came of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 不是的 我有所发现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, that's not right. Something did come of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他进了旅馆 他见了另一个半死人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He went to that hotel. He met that other dead 'un.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:57.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我偷走了所有的证据 全都串起来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I lifted the evidence off him. It all adds up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果我不逮捕他 他随时都会发起突袭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's going to pounce any minute if I don't track him down and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:02.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想错了 队长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are not thinking straight, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:04.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他不是个威胁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He is not a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,明白吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我没错 那个爱尔兰浑蛋需要人去阻止\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am thinking straight. That Irish rotter needs to be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,回家去吧 Gary\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Go home, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:19.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是命令\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:37.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,别担心 Jem 你以后不会再见到我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't worry, Jem. This is the last time you have to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Jem 你至少也正眼看我一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Jem, can you at least look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:53.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,开门\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,打开这破门 不然我就硬闯了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Open this bloody door or I'll bust it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:48.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,普天之下 莫非帝土\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}God's own country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,从Norfolk来的 不到四小时就到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Norfolk? Under four hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:00.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真是好车技啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 车开得超快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, it's quite the drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她现在还是方向盘手呢 哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her hands are still set at ten to two. Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这里有医生嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is there a doctor in the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:10.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,希望我们不用再多跑几趟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hopefully, we won't be making multiple trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:15.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很抱歉要带给你坏消息了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, sorry to be the bearer of bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我恐怕这是不可避免的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But I'm afraid it's just not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果你们给我电话 我还能提前告知你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'd have told you that over the phone, if you'd have called.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 Tom 我能叫你Tom吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, you see, Tom... Can I call you Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:26.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道 Tom 你发来的测试十分有趣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You see, Tom, the tests you sent through were very interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但想要深入了解的不止是我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but it's not just us who needs to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有Halperin&Weston公司\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's Halperin & Weston.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,大公司难免强硬\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bit of a behemoth, bit of a juggernaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:35.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 大公司 你不说我也知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Big company. Don't need to remind me of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一旦Norfolk再次进行研究项目\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Once the old ball starts rolling at Norfolk,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:38.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,恐怕很难再阻止它进行下去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}it's nigh on impossible to stop the damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在Norfolk学习过 对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You studied at Norfolk, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,确实很荣幸在那儿上过学\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I had the privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Tom 你知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, Tom, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果你肯行个方便给我们地址\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if you could do us the privilege of getting that address,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那可真是帮了大忙了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that would be a massive help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对不起 我没有地址\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sorry. I don't have the address.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:58.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真的嘛 -暂时住址还是有的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Really? - In between addresses, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:01.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那 那医疗记录上会有记录的对嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And... and the medical records would state that, would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:05.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你能给我们看嘛 不过看样子你也不打算给\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If you were to show them to us, which you're not going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:09.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我说过 我不能给你看病人的医疗记录\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Like I said, I can't show you a patient's medical records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:16.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 本希望我能帮点什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sorry. Liked to have been of more help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:20.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你也没办法啊 你又不知道Amy Dyer住哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What can you do? You don't know where Amy Dyer lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:25.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,恐怕不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们再联系吧 Tom\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We'll be in touch... Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还会喜欢我嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you still going to like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:45.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了 -现在 我 嗯 变热了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- What? - Now I'm, er... warming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:47.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你只见过我半死的状态\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You've only known me a bit deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:49.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,变热了可能你就不喜欢了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You might not like me heated up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Amy\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:57.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是冷是热我都喜欢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'd like you cold. I'd like you hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你半冷不热我都喜欢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'd even like you tepid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:04.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,无论你是生是死 你都是你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're still you, dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,懂吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了 那条路是围栏的边界\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's wrong? That way's the perimeter fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,今天有纪念重生的边界巡逻游行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Today's the Beating of the Bounds march.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,最好避开点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Best avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸 Kier之后会怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Dad, what's going to happen to Kier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:33.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他得回治疗中心待上一段时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's going to go back to the treatment centre for a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那的人会帮助他恢复原来的样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and they're going to help him get back to his old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:41.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们不会把他关起来折磨虐待吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They're not going to lock him up and do things to him, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 你怎么会这么想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. Where did you get that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:46.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他会没事的 Norfolk是个好地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He'll be all right. Norfolk's a nice place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:49.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我去边界巡逻了 他在屋里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Off to beat the bounds. He's in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,知道啦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还不错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:19.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Amy 这是游行的终点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Amy, the march ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们就待一会儿 我只是想多摸摸别的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We won't be long. I just want to touch more things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你有票的吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You've got your ticket, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:28.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 我想在委员会里还是有点好处\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. I suppose t'council were good for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Lamb夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mrs Lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:44.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,议员 或者我该说 前议员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Councillor. Or should I say ex-councillor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,祝贺你得到议员提名\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Congratulations on your nomination to the parish council.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:50.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也到时候了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's about time this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:53.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,镇子应该被敬畏神明的人民统治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}village were represented by God-fearing folk,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:57.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而不是被一些浑浑噩噩的懦夫和肮脏的变态糟蹋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}instead of just a bunch of flailing wimps and filthy perverts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,祝你今天过得愉快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:04.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hold your horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她不准进\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She's not valid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:10.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我给你票了 -你只给我了一张票\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I gave you my ticket. - You gave me a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她的票呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where's hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Lamb 如果你认真看了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mrs Lamb, if you check the fine print on the fte charter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:22.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我在职时起草的节日章程\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a charter I helped draft while I was in office,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:24.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你会看到这么一条\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you'll see a clause, and in that clause it states,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那就是 每张冬季节日票的持有者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that all ticket holders to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:29.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可以带一个伴侣入场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the winter fête are entitled to a plus-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Amy Dyer就是我的女伴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Amy Dyer's my plus-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:38.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,新议员 我可以很明确的告诉你 她可以进去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can assure you, Councillor Elect, she is valid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:44.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,边界巡逻游行在诺顿镇是一项古老的传统\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Beating the bounds is an ancient tradition here in Roarton.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很高兴大家都能来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm thrilled to see people turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,带这些真的有必要吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are all these really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,大家有点热心过头了吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think everyone's going overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:49.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我宣布Roarton的新围墙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm thrilled to announce the completion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在预算内如期完成\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}under budget and on time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,今天就将剪彩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of Roarton's new perimeter fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果没有委员会的新政策\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We couldn't have achieved this construction
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:00.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有这项政策的保证\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}without the parish council adopting new policies
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们也做不出\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that will guarantee the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:05.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,保护我们社区安全的工程\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}safety of this community for generations to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:07.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都是多亏了你啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We couldn't have done it without you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-Martin小姐 -今天重点不在我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}-Miss Martin. - Today isn't about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:14.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,重点在我们大家 着手于新的开始 新的光明\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's about all of us, embarking on a new beginning, a new dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:19.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,安全 自豪 廉洁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}protected, proud and incorruptible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:22.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在 该剪开这条彩带了 好让我们开始游行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now... I should cut this ribbon so we can get a move on, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:25.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谁有利器借我用一下吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Anyone got a sharp implement I can use?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:28.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,用这个 夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Here you are, missus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:37.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,开始游行吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So, let the march commence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这白痴又来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Here comes dickhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-嗨 -哈喽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- 'Ey up. - 'Ey up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-你可以走了 -啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Go on, then. Be off with you. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我是来代替你的 笨蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm relieving you of your post, you tart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我应该在这站岗一天的啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm supposed to be on guard duty all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:13.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我调了 这样你就能休息一天了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I've fiddled it. Thought you could do with t'day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:16.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去庆祝吧 请你喝一杯热葡萄酒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Go to t'fête. Have a mulled wine on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:20.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快去 过了这村可就没这店了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Go on, then, before I see sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:24.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢 Gaz 你真好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ta, Gaz. You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢您嘞 伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cheers, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:50.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要去哪 你个废柴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You going somewhere, dry rot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:52.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Simon在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where's Simon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:07.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-他去哪了 -我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Where is he? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说谎 你和你的小情人可是好得很呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bullshit. You and lover boy are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Gary 我都好几天没看到他了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I haven't seen him for days, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:21.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道他在策划一场袭击的吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know he's planning an attack, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:25.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他妈的就是今天 我都搞清楚了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He fucking is. Today. I've sussed it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:27.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是他行动地点的安好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is this the code for where he's going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:31.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,"死者将重生为不朽" 这是圣经里的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}"The dead shall rise again incorruptible." It's a Bible quote.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 你个混蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know that, you cheeky bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们全都认为我只是一个笨蛋 不是么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know, all of you think I'm just some dumb grunt, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Gary 我不这么认为啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't think you're dumb, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:39.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I just think you're like
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你就像其他人一样 偏执还妄想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}everyone else around here, paranoid and delusional.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:44.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们这群僵尸到处走动怎么能不多想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is it any wonder with you ghouls walking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:45.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我爸爸说过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know, my pap used to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,世上原本是没有怪物的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}say there were no such thing as monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:50.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们这群怪物出现了 就把世界弄得乌烟瘴气\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then you horror shows turn up and start tearing the world apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:53.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谁能来解决 我 只有我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And who's expected to deal with it, eh? Me, that's who.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:55.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你以为我愿意战斗吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You think I wanted to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你以为我愿意看见这些吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you think I wanted to see the things I saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:59.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Gary 正在兴头上吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You get off on all that shit, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在你们出现之前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I were ready to settle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:03.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我已经准备金盆洗手了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}down before you fucking dead-heads turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而现在 我和你妹妹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then me and your sister had
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:07.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,却不得不管这些破事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to strap on the brass and take care of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:10.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为 如果我们不管 就会死人 就死在我们的怀里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cos if we didn't, people died. In our arms, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不会再发生了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's not going to happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不会让它再发生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我最后问你一遍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So, I'm going to ask you for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爱尔兰半死人在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where's that Irish rotter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:35.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:40.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,中尉 接下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Lieutenant. Think you can
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你来带领游行的队伍好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}handle leading the march the rest of the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是队长带领吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But shouldn't the Captain lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:47.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他不是不在嘛 就由你带吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, he's not here, is he? Falls to you to take the reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:25.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-只要一个焦糖苹果 -我找给你零钱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Just one toffee apple, please. - I'll just get your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:30.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-Sue 还好吧 -嗨 Shirley\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- All right, Sue? - Oh. Hi, Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:32.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你都还好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:36.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还好 我为Philip操心的都快长溃疡了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Aye, suppose. Philip's got me sprouting ulcers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:38.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他怎么让你这么操心啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is he giving you a hard time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道 这些小孩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, you know what they're like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:43.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们到了这个年纪 就感觉像变了个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They get to a certain age, they become unrecognisable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Kieren怎么样啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How's Kieren holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:48.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 他也有点不好管了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. He's, er... being a bit difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:52.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,议会威胁他的方法真的太恶心了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Disgusting what the council's threatening to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:54.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好在他有你的支持\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good job he's got you to fight his corner.
