Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.83,0:31:36.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快醒来吧 Danny\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wake up, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.99,0:31:44.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,求求你了 Danny\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.87,0:31:45.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please.
