Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.55,0:32:05.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.91,0:32:12.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Amy 你要带我见谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Who am I meeting, Amy?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.75,0:32:34.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
