Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.27,0:32:50.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.47,0:32:54.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没事的 你没事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's all right. You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.11,0:32:57.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,－我 我刚刚有伤着人么 －没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Did I... did I hurt anyone? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.43,0:33:00.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你没有 你战胜了狂暴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, you didn't. You beat it.
