Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.23,0:33:03.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.47,0:33:08.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,站起来 我们走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's get you up. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.43,0:33:09.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没事吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.91,0:33:12.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没事的 没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's ok, it's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.19,0:33:17.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Simon 第二波重生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Simon, the second Rising...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.35,0:33:18.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不会发生了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.87,0:33:20.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那怎么可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But it's got to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.67,0:33:23.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,二次重生必须要完成\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The second Rising has to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.51,0:33:27.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,额 我的爱好就是这些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And, um... that's about it for my hobbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.39,0:33:29.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他也是一个非常棒的运动员 奶奶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's also a very good sportsman, Nan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.47,0:33:31.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,－Amy 你这样讲我多不好意思 －喔 这么羞射啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Amy, you're embarrassing me. - Aw, so modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.91,0:33:33.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.51,0:33:40.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还好么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.83,0:33:43.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I... I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.75,0:33:47.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得我的心脏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.07,0:33:54.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.83,0:33:57.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,正在跳呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.03,0:34:03.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Amy Dyer\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Amy Dyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.39,0:34:05.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是第一个也是最后一个重生之人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are the first and the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.67,0:34:08.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.35,0:34:10.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.19,0:34:18.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.63,0:34:21.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,－你想让我怎么处理这些 －锁起来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- What you want me to do with these? - Lock up after.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.39,0:34:22.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我必须去阻止他们带走kieren\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I've got to stop them taking Kieren.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.95,0:34:24.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他刚刚变狂暴了 Pearl开枪打了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He just went rabid. Pearl shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.23,0:34:30.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是Simon为他挡住了那一枪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Simon took the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.95,0:34:34.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.03,0:34:40.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.03,0:34:50.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.39,0:34:54.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我从来没见过有人能抵挡蓝色风暴的药效\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I've never seen anyone fight against Blue Oblivion before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.67,0:34:55.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.99,0:34:59.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯哼 你若能长命百岁 什么样的都能见到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, if you live long enough, you'll see all sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.43,0:35:01.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你真是个奇迹 Kieren\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're incredible, Kieren.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.87,0:35:04.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.15,0:35:07.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我 我只是不想再伤害别人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I... I'm just a person who didn't want to do any more harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.19,0:35:10.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,别把我说的这么玄乎 好么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't start getting all mystical on me, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.03,0:35:11.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不是救世主\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not the Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.87,0:35:13.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也没有超能力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't have any special powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.83,0:35:16.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不像某人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}... unlike some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.95,0:35:19.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也没有超能力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, I don't have any special powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.87,0:35:21.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你有隐形的能力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You have the power to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.79,0:35:27.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你突然走了 我掘地三尺也没有找到你 你去哪里了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You left. I searched everywhere for you. Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.03,0:35:31.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,进城了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The city.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.07,0:35:32.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.79,0:35:35.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,救命 来人救命啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Help! Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.67,0:35:37.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.83,0:35:39.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Amy\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Amy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.87,0:35:41.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.51,0:35:44.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.15,0:35:57.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,大家注意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.19,0:35:59.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.35,0:36:01.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.95,0:36:04.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都特么的给我安静下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.47,0:36:07.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.47,0:36:13.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.43,0:36:18.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我有一个消息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I... have a message of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.07,0:36:20.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,要告诉你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.71,0:36:24.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We can...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.75,0:36:29.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以战胜我们现在最大的敌人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we can conquer our greatest enemy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.71,0:36:32.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以战胜死亡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We can conquer death.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.23,0:36:33.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.27,0:36:34.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.83,0:36:39.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我弟弟年幼时就在这儿死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My brother died here when he was very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.43,0:36:43.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那是一次意外 他们说那是我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It was an accident. They said it was my...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.03,0:36:47.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,总之是起事故\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.91,0:36:50.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他本不应该 他摔倒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He shouldn't have been... He fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.91,0:36:58.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所有的 我们所做的一切错事都能够一笔勾销\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All the... the terrible things we've done can be wiped clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.11,0:37:01.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一切重新开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.63,0:37:04.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不再悲伤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No more grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.07,0:37:06.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不再内疚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No more guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.83,0:37:11.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只需等待二次重生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And all that needs to happen is the second Rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.11,0:37:12.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.75,0:37:13.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道我说过我不希望再有一次重生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know I said I didn't want
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.93,0:37:16.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是二次重生和一次重生不一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}another one but it won't be like the first Rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.11,0:37:20.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,二次重生将会带回善良和正直的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The second Rising will bring back the good and... and righteous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.71,0:37:22.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们会毫发无损的回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They'll come back whole
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.87,0:37:24.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,纯洁善良 一如从前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and... and pure
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.67,0:37:28.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一切都会变的更好 大有改观\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and everything will be better, so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.79,0:37:30.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我可以向你们保证\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.31,0:37:34.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.71,0:37:38.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的弟弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.91,0:37:42.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,被深埋地下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}... is in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.79,0:37:44.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.83,0:37:45.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,冰冷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.95,0:37:49.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,并且孤独\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}... and alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.19,0:37:51.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他不应该待在那儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He doesn't deserve to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.00,0:37:52.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他应该从土里出来和我待在一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He deserves to be up here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.99,0:37:54.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,重获新生 完好无缺\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.95,0:37:56.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.63,0:37:59.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,想要获得二次重生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The second Rising will happen
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.47,0:38:03.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,需要牺牲第一个重生者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}when the First Risen is sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.39,0:38:04.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.39,0:38:04.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.83,0:38:07.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那个门徒原本 原本是要完成这项任务的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The disciple was meant... he was meant to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.87,0:38:10.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可他没有 我 我以为是那个女孩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He didn't. I... I thought it was the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.95,0:38:13.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.11,0:38:17.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我杀了她 但是什么都没有发生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I took care of her, and nothing. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.15,0:38:20.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么都没改变\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Still nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.27,0:38:22.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.35,0:38:23.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我 呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.79,0:38:24.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.83,0:38:30.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,镇上的某个半死者一定是第一个重生的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}One of the undead in this village must be the First Risen,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.07,0:38:34.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要求你们和我一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I am asking you to join with me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.15,0:38:37.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,翻遍所有角落把他找出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in leaving no stone unturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.35,0:38:43.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,镇上所有半死症患者都应被处决\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Every PDS sufferer in Roarton must be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.31,0:38:45.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.35,0:38:51.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,刻不容缓\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.99,0:38:55.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.15,0:38:56.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.95,0:39:02.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.03,0:39:04.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.55,0:39:07.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-她疯了         -你说的真对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- She's tapped. - You're right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.35,0:39:10.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们当时在墓地里 然后Martin小姐走过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We were at the graveyard and Miss Martin comes up to us
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.23,0:39:11.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-说一些关于\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- and says something about
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.60,0:39:13.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Amy是第一个也是最后一个什么的  -噢 天哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Amy being the first and the last. - Oh! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.91,0:39:17.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-接着Maxine刺伤了她 -她竟然在流血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- And then Maxine just stabbed her. - She's bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.15,0:39:19.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-你赶快做点什么 -我不明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- You've got to do something. - I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.87,0:39:22.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-Amy 不要啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Amy, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.51,0:39:24.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.11,0:39:25.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不要啊 Amy\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please, Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.23,0:39:28.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不可以就这样离开我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're not allowed to leave like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.27,0:39:31.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是我永远最好的朋友 知道么 永远最好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're my best dead friend for ever. Ok? Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.23,0:39:33.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你 你一定要做到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That is... that is non-negotiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.07,0:39:34.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.35,0:39:40.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-她失血过多了 -请你救救她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- She's lost too much blood. - You've got to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.67,0:39:44.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她的瞳孔放大了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her pupils have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.63,0:40:02.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你站着干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.43,0:40:06.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.27,0:40:09.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.35,0:40:11.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不会的 她才不会死的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.43,0:40:14.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.51,0:40:30.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.67,0:41:18.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的衣服呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where's your outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.75,0:41:20.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在我房间里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.35,0:41:28.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,葬礼上所有人都得穿时髦漂亮的衣服\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Everyone at the funeral has to wear classy, more-geous outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.43,0:41:32.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不能穿死板的黑色西装和裙子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No boring black suits or dresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.11,0:41:36.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是她所要的超级酷的送别\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's part of her "Totally cool send-off".
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.03,0:41:41.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道我是不是应该去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't even know if I should be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.47,0:41:44.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当然 你要去 你可是在贵宾名单上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, you should. You're on the VIP guest list.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.59,0:41:51.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.19,0:41:52.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可他不能来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's not invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.35,0:42:03.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们分手了 我甩了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We broke up. I broke up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.71,0:42:09.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果他和你是对立的 我会选择你这边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If it's his word against yours, then I choose yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.51,0:42:23.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.17,0:42:24.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.31,0:44:07.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我听说Maxine Martin被送去精神病院了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I heard Maxine Martin's been committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.19,0:44:10.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.19,0:44:17.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-Philip在哪儿 -他不肯离开她的墓地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Where's Philip? - He won't leave her graveside.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.07,0:44:20.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,人总要有些念想的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You've got to have faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.43,0:44:21.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.75,0:45:05.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.99,0:45:08.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我这辈子不会给他们投票了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am never voting for them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.55,0:45:11.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.99,0:45:15.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就该这样 噢 我们打算就这么玩 对吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's it. Oh, we're going to play it like that, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.59,0:45:17.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对啊 好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Right. Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.67,0:45:33.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道你们还可以喝东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I didn't know your kind could drink liquids.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.47,0:45:36.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是不能 只是喝点下去别人就会感觉轻松点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We can't. Just getting 'em in so people feel comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.47,0:45:38.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 亲爱的 你阵体贴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, that's very considerate of you, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.99,0:45:43.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那些针眼瞳孔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Those pinprick eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.95,0:45:48.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-让我觉得都快吐了 -噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I were almost sick in me mouth. - Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.03,0:45:50.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信Pearl会让那些家伙进来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can't believe Pearl lets those things in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.43,0:45:52.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她只是心怀愧疚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She only does it out of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.11,0:45:54.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我才不管发生了什么 废物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't care what happened. A rotter...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.79,0:45:57.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-永远是废物 -你说对了 亲爱的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Is a rotter. - You said it, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.19,0:46:01.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那些活人真恶心 我都想把胆汁吐出来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The living make me want to puke black bile.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.79,0:46:03.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,活人渣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Pulse-beating scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.43,0:46:05.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想我们也只能做二等公民了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I guess we're stuck here existing next to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.47,0:46:06.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.71,0:46:07.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这种日子不会太长了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.99,0:46:10.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你从先知那儿听到的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You heard from the Prophet?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.07,0:46:11.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他说了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.87,0:46:14.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Simon是叛徒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Simon's a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.19,0:46:15.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那么第二次重生呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What about the second Rising?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.99,0:46:19.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,第一个重生的人还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The First Risen's still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.15,0:47:17.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.95,0:47:23.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-嘿 -嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.83,0:47:25.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是你的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.11,0:47:29.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,曾经是 Gary送给我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Used to be. Present from Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.87,0:47:34.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-他从哪里弄的 -他给我做的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- How did he get it? - He made it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.47,0:47:36.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是的 Jem\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, Jem.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.63,0:47:42.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这个手链是Henry Lonsdale给你做的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Henry Lonsdale made this bracelet for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.19,0:47:44.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他在他消失的那晚还给我看的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He showed it to me the night he disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.75,0:47:48.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.71,0:47:59.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道他出了什么事吗 Jem\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you know what happened to him, Jem?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.07,0:48:03.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.35,0:48:04.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.43,0:48:06.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那 那只是个意外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It... it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.55,0:48:11.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那晚很黑 我在树林里夜巡 我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It was dark, I was on patrol in the woods, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.47,0:48:13.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我以为他是个狂暴丧尸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought he was rabid.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.19,0:48:23.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你想怎么做 Jem\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do you want to do, Jem?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.91,0:48:27.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想我需要点帮助 Kier\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think I need some help, Kier.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.07,0:48:28.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好 好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok. Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.31,0:48:31.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.39,0:48:33.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们会给你帮助的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's get you some help, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.79,0:48:39.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.19,0:48:44.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.91,0:48:47.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去见一下我的父母\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come and see Mum and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.47,0:48:48.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.79,0:48:51.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们认为是我的错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.15,0:48:54.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-不 他们不会 -如果Amy没有跟我一起回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- No, they don't. - If Amy hadn't have come back here with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.19,0:48:55.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 这不是你的错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.83,0:49:01.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Maxine Martin因为一些疯狂的念头 杀了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maxine Martin killed her over some... insane belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.79,0:49:06.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,呵\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.55,0:49:08.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,葬礼结束后 我们就该走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}After this, we should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.79,0:49:11.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,走 去哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Go? Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.67,0:49:13.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,离开这块地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.91,0:49:16.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这里一点都不安全 Kieren\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's not safe, Kieren.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.47,0:49:20.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不能走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.91,0:49:25.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-你不是一直想要离开吗 -是的 原本是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Isn't leaving what you wanted to do? - Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.99,0:49:27.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Amy曾经问我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Amy once asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.59,0:49:31.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要走多远才能接受自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}how many miles I'd have to go before I could be ok with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.87,0:49:34.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我本来想可能我得走遍全世界\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought I'd have to go around the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.67,0:49:38.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是我现在不那么想了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I don't think that any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.47,0:49:42.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我在这儿活得不错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm ok here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.71,0:49:46.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.51,0:49:49.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.35,0:49:51.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Simon\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.75,0:49:53.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要感谢你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.99,0:49:57.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-感谢我什么 -你救了Kier\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Thank me? - You saved Kier's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.31,0:50:04.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,本能反应罢了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.99,0:50:09.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你有住的地方吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Have you got somewhere to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.59,0:50:11.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的 有 我 我暂时住在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Yeah, I'm... I'm staying
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.62,0:50:14.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,Amy的小屋里 所以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}up at Amy's bungalow at the moment, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.39,0:50:15.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不准备走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not going away, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.11,0:50:21.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.15,0:50:22.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我会留在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I'm staying put.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.71,0:51:25.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.83,0:51:51.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,终于走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.91,0:52:01.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有时间吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is there still time?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.39,0:52:05.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.59,0:52:16.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把它装起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bag it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.00,0:52:53.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
